Kandipa pondati pecha kelunga. Kooda porandha thangachi ya seruppaala adicha kooda pondati pecha kelunga. Kadaisi varai varapporadhu pondati thaan. Pondati thappe pannalum pondati pecha kelunga. Kooda porandha thangachi thappe pannalanaalum avala seruppaala adicha kooda thappe illai. Adhuvum kooda porandha thangachi ku Appa illa na keka naadi ye illai.
